reviewText: This was a used tape, but watchable. Hoping to get it on DVD someday.

I am a huge fan of Nick Lea so, even though this film is formulaic and silly, it's worth watching just for Nick.  He's very good and *so* adorable!  He shows a real talent for comedy and it was nice to see the  lighter side of his incredible acting ability.  I must admit that if Nick  weren't in it, I would not buy it, but if you're a Nicknik, it'll be a  great addition to your collection :)
